{"tid":1246273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大家黎睇睇】到而家呢一步最大問題係如何延續運動及民氣","createTime":"2019-06-20T15:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T02:47:05.000Z","uid":139095,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"613718c6c1c75fd83f1d878554766355fd2b2c85","tid":1246273,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"林鄭一直冷處理落去，我地好快會散。<br />\n不論係有人分化定係被時間沖淡。<br />\n<br />\n所以比起要林鄭回應訴求，更<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">重要</span></span>係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係如何延續運動及民氣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家討論去邊野餐都好<br />\n<br />\n其實諗深一層，其實有冇實際效果係其次，&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">重點係keep住股氣勢。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然拖係冇乜好處，但至少可以拖到g20<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點</span></span>(分先後)<br />\n1.保持國外及本地傳媒關注，給外國施加壓力必須表態<br />\n2.保持氣勢至g20後，減內耗<br />\n3.五(或四)點訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有在鏡頭之下才能保護示威者</span>"},{"pid":"4127276bbfd7deb59970a7eb4d9de198a5e12c0a","tid":1246273,"uid":139095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38407720ca13a3f8b6152cbea34c0e517dcbf319","tid":1246273,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"要大家化整為零有d難，你睇下雨傘後d鳩嗚團根本就make 唔到noise"},{"pid":"bc4a1138e4f7c5ff22fdc50e07e1a0d35b744494","tid":1246273,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4127276bbfd7deb59970a7eb4d9de198a5e12c0a","tid":1246273,"uid":139095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"81c86ccc583c13019e7fde6c01e155f08345f370","tid":1246273,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集思廣益</span></span>"},{"pid"